2026-07-11 12:48:50,799 [INFO] Done:
Race selection is now wired into the game flow: **class select → race select → mastery picker**. `class_select.gd` spawns `race_select.gd` right after a class is chosen, and `race_select.gd`'s confirm handler (already built to do this) calls `GameState.choose_race()` and then spawns the Mastery Picker. I also committed the previously-uncommitted race backend it depends on (`Stats` race fields/`apply_race_defaults`, `GameState.race_picker_open` input-gating, darkvision FOV hook, Elf shorter rests) and updated both CLAUDE.md docs. Pushed to `main`.

Remaining deferred pieces (Halfling nat-1 reroll, Human miss-reroll, Elf sub-race spell, Dragonborn breath weapon) are left as-is per your note that they're cosmetic for now.

